title: 65DaysOfWarOfTheWorlds
description:
A fan-made album where a recorded reading of H.G. Wells' novel 'The War of the Worlds' has been dubbed over 65daysofstatic's album 'The Fall of Math'.

The album plays through track by track apart from 'Default This' (the 4th song) which is at the end. It's not an entire reading of the novel but there is enough there to make the story coherent.

This is not my work and unfortunately I am unable to credit the person who made it, I have no idea who it was.

1. 0:00 - Another Code Against the Gone
2. 1:40 - Install a Beak In the Heart That Clucks Time In Arabic
3. 6:35 - Retreat! Retreat!
4. 11:37 - I Swallowed Hard, Like I Understood
5. 17:05 - The Fall of Math
6. 21:05 - This Cat Is a Landmine
7. 25:50 - The Last Home Recording
8. 28:03 - Hole
9. 32:37 - Fix the Sky a Little
10. 38:07 - Aren't We All Running
11. 42:58 - Default This
